episodes.title: Episode 1
episodes.description: DCI Carl Morck returns to work after a near-fatal incident and finds himself head of a new department. A prosecutor faces a tough day in court.

episodes.title: Episode 2
episodes.description: As Carl and his new assistant start digging into their first cold case, he can't stop his personal demons encroaching on his professional life.

episodes.title: Episode 3
episodes.description: Carl and Akram recreate the fateful ferry journey on their way to the Isle of Mhòr. A frustrated Rose makes her case for joining their Department.

episodes.title: Episode 4
episodes.description: Rose goes to the island to find out what Carl couldn't. Akram finds a note which sends the investigation in an entirely new direction.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: The prosecutor's disappearance becomes connected with a death. A scuffle in a newspaper office sees Carl making headlines, and Moira sees a therapist.

episodes.title: Episode 6
episodes.description: The police detain a suspect for the Leith Park shooting. Carl returns to the scene of the crime, before losing his temper in public once again.

episodes.title: Episode 7
episodes.description: Carl makes some dangerous allegations to some powerful men, while Rose takes a fresh angle to uncover more information about Sam Haig.

episodes.title: Episode 8
episodes.description: The kidnappers give their victim a clue as they press her for an answer to their question. Dept. Q gets closer to unravelling its own riddle.

episodes.title: Episode 9
episodes.description: A decades-old recording helps all the clues to fall into place. But as the pressure rises — in and out of the chamber — can Carl get there in time?

episodes.title: Episode 7
episodes.description: Episode 7 of Dept. Q

episodes.title: The Pink Marine
episodes.description: Without telling his mother, earnest teen Cameron impulsively follows his best friend Ray into the unforgiving gauntlet of Marine Corps boot camp.

episodes.title: The Buddy System
episodes.description: A training exercise strains Cameron's bond with Ray and forces brothers John and Cody to unpack the family baggage they brought to Parris Island.

episodes.title: The Confidence Course
episodes.description: Cameron digs deep to prove himself in a confidence-building course. The platoon receives a late addition. Barbara discovers sympathy has its perks.

episodes.title: Sink or Swim
episodes.description: Amid a high-pressure week of swim training, Ray struggles to stay afloat — until Cameron dives in with a risky scheme to keep him above water.

episodes.title: Bullseye
episodes.description: Emotions run high as Cameron and the recruits aim to hit their marks in rifle training. Sgt. Sullivan lands in a very different set of crosshairs.

episodes.title: The Things We Carry
episodes.description: The platoon grapples with the cost of being a Marine. Capt. Fajardo brings Staff Sgt. McKinnon up to speed. The mess hall lives up to its name.

episodes.title: Love Is a Battlefield
episodes.description: As combat training begins, a brutal mind game drives a recruit to the breaking point. A violation of protocol stirs trouble in the ranks.

episodes.title: The Crucible
episodes.description: The recruits face the ultimate test as the Crucible pushes the limits of their endurance — and brotherhood is the only way to get past the finish line

episodes.title: Episode 1
episodes.description: When a neighbor's au pair vanishes after asking to talk with her, Cecilie feels responsible — compelling her to personally investigate.

episodes.title: Episode 2
episodes.description: After finding potential evidence, Cecile grows suspicious of Rasmus. Assigned to Ruby's case, police officer Aicha gets in over her head.

episodes.title: Episode 3
episodes.description: Cecilie secretly shares her discovery with Aicha. Viggo's friends pressure him to share inappropriate videos in their group chat.

episodes.title: Episode 4
episodes.description: A break in the investigation leads Aicha to suspect the worst. Cecilie is suspicious of Mike after finding questionable information on his phone.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Katarina asks Cecilie to help her with a painful task. Aicha is told to drop the case, fueling her determination to dig deeper.

episodes.title: Episode 6
episodes.description: As those around her twist the narrative to their benefit, Cecilie is left wondering who she's really dealing with.

episodes.title: Tum Mujhpe Bharosa Karti Ho?
episodes.description: Aarya and Tej's family life turns upside down when her brother, Sangram, and their friend, Jawahar, take a dangerous risk to make a quick buck.

episodes.title: Aapko Shaq Hai Kisi Par?
episodes.description: Tragedy strikes home. Adding insult to injury, Aarya has to deal with an unforeseen pressure from the police. In the midst of all this, Aarya begins to suspect someone.

episodes.title: Kaun Zimmedar Hai?
episodes.description: While the family reels in distress, Jawahar warns Aarya about the danger they all are in. When she visits Sangram in the jail, a shock awaits her.

episodes.title: Apne Panje Bahar Nikaalo
episodes.description: Aarya is threatened by an unknown assailant, which ups her worry about her children's safety, who are dealing with their own problems. But she finds an unlikely ally in Daulat.

episodes.title: Kaun Chalaega Business?
episodes.description: Danger strikes Aarya and her family once more, and the relentless Khan searches her house yet again. Fed up, Aarya decides to take the bull by the horns and meets Shekhawat.

episodes.title: Ek Guru Chahiye
episodes.description: As Aarya dives deep into the business, she faces her first challenge. In the meantime, Khan goes after Hina for information, while Jawahar and Daulat get into a scuffle.

episodes.title: Aapki Mummy Don Hai
episodes.description: The worst has happened and Aarya goes looking for Jawahar. Distressed, she informs Shekhawat about a change in plan, only to find him uncaring. How will she keep her kids safe?

episodes.title: Grahan Hai Aaj
episodes.description: Aarya shares with Veer and Aru the challenges she has been facing, and promises to end all the suffering with a master plan. Will everything fall into place?

episodes.title: Dharm Sankat
episodes.description: Despite losing the case, Khan is adamant to find the truth. As another tragedy strikes and the family is in the depths of despair, Aarya is left with a fresh dilemma.

episodes.title: Mujhe Yahaan Se Bhaagna Hai
episodes.description: Forced to return to testify against her family, Aarya is caught in a whirlwind of her bloodied past, the one she has been running away from.

episodes.title: An Eye For An Eye
episodes.description: Aarya drowns in the fear of being attacked by her enemies as she tries to find ways to run away from the country. However, someone is keeping an eye on her.

episodes.title: Ab Hum Vaapis Jaa Rahe Hain
episodes.description: Aarya's past returns to help her in restoring normalcy, and her plans to escape seem to be taking shape. But an unexpected event may create new obstacles.

episodes.title: Sangram Kahaan Hai?
episodes.description: Sangram's disappearance becomes a hurdle to Aarya's plans. Meanwhile, Hina reveals something unpleasant to Aarya.

episodes.title: 300 Crore Ka Consignment
episodes.description: As another tragedy shakes her family, Aarya is shocked to find the Rs 300 crore consignment returned to her life.

episodes.title: I Hate You, Mom
episodes.description: The Sareen family struggles to stay united. In this true test of time, what will Aarya lose next?

episodes.title: Phir Se Panje Baahar Nikaalo
episodes.description: As Hina spirals in her grief, Aarya is pushed to the brink by the Russians and Shekhawat. Will she seek Daulat's help?

episodes.title: Isko Mere Raaste Se Hataa Do
episodes.description: When an unexpected outcome shakes her conscience, Aarya realises she can't run away from her reality. A final confrontation turns her into someone she never thought she would be.

episodes.title: Episode 9
episodes.description: Episode 9 of Aarya

episodes.title: Galti Ki Saza Maut
episodes.description: Aarya faces the impossible choice between protecting her son's love and protecting her family from the Russians. Meanwhile, Sooraj tortures Roop to ensure Aarya's destruction.

episodes.title: Sherni Ka Shikar
episodes.description: Dangerous heroin suppliers Nalini Sahiba and Abhimanyu threaten Aarya if the consignment is not retrieved. As Aarya hunts for Sooraj, she struggles with her sons and Khan.

episodes.title: Bali Ya Balidaan
episodes.description: Sooraj's quest to find Nandini's remains pushes him to extreme lengths. In the meantime, Veer, Maya, Aarya and Sooraj find themselves bound by revenge and regret.

episodes.title: Sherni Ke Shikaar Ka Waqt Aa Gaya Hai
episodes.description: Thanks to the seized consignment, Aarya and Nalini Sahiba end up in the crosshairs of Mikhail, the new Russian boss. Betrayals come to light, and a crucial meeting turns bloody.

episodes.title: Khabri Ki Sazaa Maut
episodes.description: Daulat abandons his new life to help Aarya again. Sampat faces Aarya's wrath for shooting Dhruv, but Aru blames her. Nalini Sahiba and Mikhail put Aarya in a tight spot.

episodes.title: Aarya Sareen Is An Unfit Mother
episodes.description: The welfare officer finally meets the whole family. However, an unpleasant interruption becomes disastrous. As business and family collide, how will Aarya protect her loved ones?

episodes.title: Panje Nikalne Ka Waqt Aa Gaya Hai
episodes.description: Having lost everything she holds dear, Aarya takes an inevitable step. Caught between the Russians, Nalini Sahiba and Khan, how will Aarya redeem herself?

episodes.title: Stick or Twist
episodes.description: Harry Da Souza is called upon to make a problem disappear.

episodes.title: Jigsaw Puzzle
episodes.description: Harry must deal with the aftermath of the Harrigan family meeting.

episodes.title: Plan B
episodes.description: Richie makes his move, putting the Harrigans on high alert.

episodes.title: Rat Trap
episodes.description: Conrad comes to Jan for a favor. Kevin makes a confession to Harry.

episodes.title: Funeral for a Friend
episodes.description: Kevin and Harry assess scenarios in a search for insurance and an exit strategy.

episodes.title: Antwerp Blues
episodes.description: Conrad twists the knife as Maeve gives Eddie a lesson in the art of chess.

episodes.title: The Crossroads
episodes.description: O'Hara points out the elephant in the room. Harry takes extreme measures.

episodes.title: Helter Skelter
episodes.description: Maeve extends an olive branch. Richie contemplates a new affiliation.

episodes.title: Beggars Banquet
episodes.description: Tattersall gets Alice's tootsies tapping. Kevin confronts his past.

episodes.title: The Beast in Me
episodes.description: Kevin takes care of a problem. Maeve spills the tea.

episodes.title: Maine Dekhi Hai Uski Mrityu
episodes.description: Juhi, Rhea's Hindi literature professor, suspects her of cheating in her term essay and fails her. Later, Rhea manipulates Arun, the hostel security guard, to get Juhi’s address.

episodes.title: Nishaane Pe Sirf Main Thi
episodes.description: Juhi and Neil’s relationship begins to fall through the cracks. Juhi and Rhea's rivalry becomes public after she deliberately humiliates Rhea in class. Rhea visits Juhi's house and meets Neil.

episodes.title: Sach Ke Kai Pehlu
episodes.description: Juhi becomes increasingly suspicious about Rhea after she loses her wedding ring. She notices Rhea wearing her wedding ring and attacks her at the founder's day party. Neil and Juhi have a huge fight.

episodes.title: Sach Ki Tarah Log Bhi Complex Hote Hain
episodes.description: Juhi goes through emotional turmoil and seeks support from her parents. Anand pays a visit to Rhea. Rhea seduces Neil while Juhi is at her parents' anniversary party.

episodes.title: Hum Sab Mein Ek Cheat Hota Hai
episodes.description: Neil shows Juhi the picture he found in his pocket. Juhi confronts Anand about the picture and he confesses the truth about Rhea. Rhea reveals her past to Neil. Juhi returns home to a shocking sight.

episodes.title: Tum Phool Si, Main Kaante Si
episodes.description: Sunanda is convinced that there is more to the story and digs deeper into Rhea's life. Anand manages to get Rhea to confess her crime. Rhea attempts to reach out to Juhi, but her hopes are shattered.

episodes.title: Chehre Pe Chehra
episodes.description: Juhi is accused of plagiarism by Amit Chaudhary. She suspects Rhea to be behind the allegation. Meanwhile, Rhea’s plan to inherit the Rajguru estate is at risk. A shocking revelation awaits Anand.

episodes.title: We Are Family
episodes.description: Amit serves a legal notice to Juhi through Anand. Anand’s attempt to meet Amit and resolve the matter only complicates it further. On the other hand, Rhea learns about Juhi’s past with Vishal.

episodes.title: The Darkest Hour
episodes.description: Juhi learns about Anand’s confession of plagiarising from Amit and publicly takes the blame to protect Anand. A guilt-ridden Anand apologizes to Juhi and Rhea before taking a drastic step.

episodes.title: I Will Never Stop
episodes.description: Juhi tries to find the truth behind the plagiarism allegations. Meanwhile, Rhea searches for Yash's real father. When Yash goes missing, Juhi suspects Rhea and takes the police to the Rajguru estate.

episodes.title: Jo Karna Tha, Mujhe Karna Tha
episodes.description: Arun's obsession endangers Yash, forcing Rhea and Amit to fight him. Juhi gets admitted to a mental facility after hearing of Yash's death. Amit becomes fearful of Rhea's ambitions.

episodes.title: Tum Aur Main Alag Nahi
episodes.description: Amit tells Juhi that Yash is alive and with Rhea. Juhi tricks Rhea to continue her search for Yash at the Rajguru estate. A final confrontation with Rhea forces Juhi to turn the tables.

episodes.title: Descenso
episodes.description: Chilean drug chemist Cockroach brings his product to Colombian smuggler Pablo Escobar. DEA agent Steve Murphy joins the war on drugs in Bogota.

episodes.title: The Sword of Simón Bolívar
episodes.description: Communist radical group M-19 makes a move against the narcos, while Murphy gets an education in Colombian law enforcement from his new partner Peña.

episodes.title: The Men of Always
episodes.description: Murphy encounters the depths of government corruption when he and Peña try to derail Escobar's political ambitions by proving he's a narco.

episodes.title: The Palace in Flames
episodes.description: Despite a new extradition treaty, the U.S. puts more money into fighting communism, creating new challenges for Murphy and Peña in the hunt for Pablo.

episodes.title: There Will Be a Future
episodes.description: Pablo's extreme methods put the narcos on the brink of war with Carillo and  the government. Peña tries to protect his witness, Elisa.

episodes.title: Explosivos
episodes.description: Peña and Carillo close in on Gacha, while Murphy tries to protect pro-extradition candidate Gaviria from a notorious assassin connected to Pablo.

episodes.title: You Will Cry Tears of Blood
episodes.description: Pablo goes into hiding as the political tide turns against him, but he finds a way to strike back. Murphy and Peña finally get the CIA to help them.

episodes.title: La Gran Mentira
episodes.description: A tragic mistake forces the government to change tactics in the fight against Pablo. But Pablo faces bigger threats from inside his empire.

episodes.title: Free at Last
episodes.description: In the aftermath of a massive military effort to take Pablo into custody, the family reunites while enemies worry. Steve and Connie fight about safety.

episodes.title: Cambalache
episodes.description: Tata gets impatient with life on the run. Pablo responds to President Gaviria's reward offer. Steve and Javier meet their new boss.

episodes.title: Our Man in Madrid
episodes.description: President Gaviria has a new job for an old colleague. The Search Bloc's new tactics shake up Pablo, but also unsettle Steve and Javier.

episodes.title: The Good, The Bad, and The Dead
episodes.description: The Cali cartel discusses moving in on Pablo's territory. Limón proposes a plan to Maritza. Tata gets a gun for protection.

episodes.title: The Enemies of My Enemy
episodes.description: The Search Bloc gets a new leader. Javier loses faith in the system. Pablo brings Tata's brother Carlos down from Miami to cheer her up.

episodes.title: Los Pepes
episodes.description: The newly-formed Los Pepes want to destroy Pablo and his empire. Tata's brother urges her to leave and seek safety with her children.

episodes.title: Mirror Faces
episodes.description: Adjusting to a new home and high school after her mom's death leads Elodie back into her comfort zone -- and into a competition with Tabitha and Moe.

episodes.title: Paper Tiger
episodes.description: An invitation to a club may provide a cure-all for Elodie's homesickness, Tabitha's growing disenchantment with her boyfriend and Moe's empty house.

episodes.title: P*ssy Palace
episodes.description: A community service day at school presents an unexpected chance for Elodie, Tabitha and Moe to bond as they check out some intriguing merchandise.

episodes.title: Happy F**king Birthday
episodes.description: Amid growing doubts about her boyfriend, Tabitha puts on a happy face for her 17th birthday. Meanwhile, Moe encourages Elodie to spread her wings.

episodes.title: Big Mistake
episodes.description: Elodie, Tabitha and Moe band together in order to retrieve a treasured keepsake, but their mischief quickly takes a turn into real trouble.

episodes.title: Rearview Mirror
episodes.description: As Elodie hits the mall to deal with her grief, Moe questions her relationship with Noah, and Tabitha gets fed up with everyone's expectations.

episodes.title: Truth Serum
episodes.description: A house party gives Elodie, Tabitha and Moe an opportunity to cut loose, but a shocking confession threatens to derail their friendship.

episodes.title: Monday I'm in Love
episodes.description: With the afternoon off from school, Elodie reconnects with her crush, Tabitha goes shopping with a friend, and Moe spends time with Noah.

episodes.title: Night Market
episodes.description: When a five-finger discount at a school event results in potentially serious consequences for Elodie, she turns to Tabitha and Moe for help.

episodes.title: The Great Escape
episodes.description: The trio deal with demands, disappointments and decisions as Brady puts the squeeze on Tabitha, Moe lashes out, and Elodie receives a tempting offer.

episodes.title: Supernova
episodes.description: With Moe and Tabitha dodging questions about her whereabouts, Elodie experiences the highs and lows of life on the road with the flighty Sabine.

episodes.title: Last Night of Freedom
episodes.description: Anxious about returning home, Elodie instead enjoys some sticky-fingered bonding with her best friends. Meanwhile, Moe's impetuousness causes concern.

episodes.title: Disconnected
episodes.description: Moe's relationship with Tabitha wobbles when a secret is accidentally revealed, and Elodie looks for an after-school activity to placate her dad.

episodes.title: Ghouls Just Wanna Have Fun
episodes.description: Being grounded doesn't stop Elodie from trying to bump into her crush at a Halloween party or asking Moe and Tabitha along to be her costumed backup.

episodes.title: Works in Progress
episodes.description: Moe struggles to be the kind of girlfriend Noah needs, Tabitha feels stung after being racially profiled, and Elodie takes a chance with Jillian.

episodes.title: Ocean's 11th Grade
episodes.description: As Elodie marks a milestone in her personal growth, Moe contends with a blackmail scheme during a robotics competition.

episodes.title: Same Time Last Year
episodes.description: An impromptu Thanksgiving gathering serves up a surprise guest, a secret romance and a host of bittersweet memories for Elodie, Tabitha and Moe.

episodes.title: Black Friday
episodes.description: Elodie's musical debut sets the stage for drama as Moe and Tabitha reckon with mutual family dysfunction and their own fraught friendship.

episodes.title: Aren't You Gonna Say Something?
episodes.description: Fallout from the stolen test plagues Moe, a meetup with Sabine robs Elodie of something precious, and a chance meeting with an ex opens Tabitha's eyes.

episodes.title: We Belong
episodes.description: In a risky gambit that they hope will heal past hurts and help them move forward together, the trio plans one last epic crime.

episodes.title: Episode 7
episodes.description: Episode 7 of Trinkets

episodes.title: Hana and Mizuki
episodes.description: Hana's love of storytelling draws the attention of the Broadcasting Club's president, Mizuki, who tries to recruit her. However, Hana has reasons to decline her offer.

episodes.title: Interest and Talent
episodes.description: The new club members must take turns introducing one another, causing Hana to wonder what her strengths are.

episodes.title: Dreams and a Sleepover
episodes.description: Hana's enthusiasm deflates as Mr. Kichijoji readies the club for an upcoming competition. Why must she want to win? Why can't she just enjoy doing what she loves?

episodes.title: A First and a Friend
episodes.description: A spontaneous question causes Hana to freeze during her first broadcast. It's one thing to stick to the script. But improvising? That's a completely different story.

episodes.title: Blue Spring and an Umbrella
episodes.description: Anne is realistic, while Hana is idealistic; disagreements are inevitable. However, that won't stop Hana from trying to befriend her fellow club member.

episodes.title: Scripts and a Pancake
episodes.description: The club members decide on what category they will each compete in at the Kyoto NHK Cup preliminaries, recitation or announcing. Toga will not enter in either.

episodes.title: Big Sister and Little Brother
episodes.description: It’s a tight deadline, but the broadcasting club has the will to complete their submission to the original TV drama category.

episodes.title: Satisfaction and Unfinished
episodes.description: Shura is an expert storyteller, and her ability to conjure an entire city in her audience’s mind proves that Hana still has a long way to go.

Viserys hosts a tournament to celebrate the birth of his second child. Rhaenyra welcomes her uncle Daemon back to the Red Keep.
episodes.title: The Heirs of the Dragon

episodes.description: Princess Rhaenyra dives deep into the prophecies about House Targaryen while confronting a realm that resists the idea of a woman on the Iron Throne, and Prince Daemon, embittered over being passed over as the heir to Westeros, prepares to go to war.
episodes.title: The Rogue Prince

episodes.description: Daemon and the Sea Snake battle the Crabfeeder. The realm celebrates Aegon's second nameday. Rhaenyra faces the prospect of marriage.
episodes.title: Second of His Name

episodes.description: Daemon returns to court after the successful completion of the battle. Princess Rhaenyra must deal with potential suitors in order to keep her line of succession.
episodes.title: King of the Narrow Sea

episodes.description: Daemon visits his wife in the Vale. Viserys and Rhaenyra broker agreements with the Valeryons. Alicent seeks the truth about the princess.
episodes.title: We Light the Way

episodes.description: Ten years later. Rhaenyra navigates Alicent's continued speculation about her children, while Daemon and Laena weigh an offer in Pentos.
episodes.title: The Princess and the Queen

episodes.description: As the families gather on Driftmark for a funeral, Viserys calls for an end to infighting and Alicent demands justice.
episodes.title: Driftmark

episodes.description: Six years later. With the Driftmark succession suddenly critical, Rhaenyra attempts to strike a bargain with Rhaenys.
episodes.title: The Lord of the Tides

episodes.description: While Alicent enlists Cole and Aemond to track down Aegon, Otto gathers the great houses of Westeros to affirm their allegiance.
episodes.title: The Green Council

episodes.description: Mourning a tragic death, Rhaenyra tries to hold the kingdom together and Daemon prepares for war.
episodes.title: The Black Queen
The Cyclone
episodes.description: Awaiting a make-or-break visit from a food critic, restaurateur Jake Friedken is thrown off-center by the return of his troublesome brother, Vince.

episodes.title: The Black Rabbits
episodes.description: Riding high, Jake begins to dream of a second restaurant — until a financial curveball puts both him and Vince in jeopardy with their creditors.

episodes.title: Skin Contact
episodes.description: When Jake and Vince throw a lavish last-minute fundraiser, Roxie suspects an ulterior motive. A disgruntled former employee rears his head.

episodes.title: No More F**k-Ups
episodes.description: Jake scrambles to conceal the truth after a reporter starts snooping around the Rabbit. A moment of overconfidence puts Vince in even deeper danger.

episodes.title: Trailblazer
episodes.description: When Junior and Babbit turn up the heat, the brothers respond in kind. Roxie appeals to Wes to make changes at the restaurant.

episodes.title: Attaf**kinboy
episodes.description: As deals, debts and double-crosses intensify, all roads lead to one fateful night at the Rabbit.

episodes.title: These Kids Nearly Got Munsoned
episodes.description: A furious Mancuso vows to settle the score with Vince. Jake faces tough questions from every direction. Estelle wrestles with guilt.

episodes.title: Isle of Joy
episodes.description: With threats closing in on all sides, the brothers make a final bid for survival that brings them face-to-face with their complicated past.

episodes.title: Episode 1
episodes.description: After her adoptive mother's death, criminologist Lejla returns to her secluded hometown, where the disappearance of a young girl tears open old wounds.

episodes.title: Episode 2
episodes.description: Lejla and Valter team up to investigate Alicia's disappearance on their own, leading to a heated argument with new police chief Tomas.

episodes.title: Episode 3
episodes.description: Frustrated with the gaps in her memory, Lejla digs deeper into her past. A wastewater leak from the mine expansion turns Said into a target.

episodes.title: Episode 4
episodes.description: As the kidnapper's profile begins to take shape, Lejla uncovers a disturbing pattern. A cozy date with Martin may not be all that it seems.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Excluded and undermined at every turn, Tomas resorts to drowning his sorrows. Lejla withdraws into herself as she deals with everything that happened.

episodes.title: Episode 6
episodes.description: Finding herself deep inside the lion's den, Lejla learns the terrible truth behind her own abduction.

episodes.title: Paisa Kamaya Nahin Banaya Jata Hain
episodes.description: A job opportunity brings Abdul Karim Telgi, a fruit seller from Khanpur, to Bombay. When he is arrested for forgery nine years later, he meets Kaushal Jhaveri in prison and joins his gum wash operation. However, fining the business unscalable, Abdul comes up with the idea to pivot into the world of stamp papers.

episodes.title: Choomantar
episodes.description: Abdul successfully begins to steal official stamp papers from trains, but needs a licence to sell them in bulk. Against Kaushal’s wishes, he uses political connections to try and acquire one from the Old Custom House but fails. To make matters worse, Kaushal, feeling betrayed, leaves Abdul’s side.

episodes.title: Khota Sikka
episodes.description: Abdul manages to acquire a license through political contacts but turns his back on the minister that helped him by allying with the new party in power. He ends up losing his license and going back to prison, where he meets a mechanic from Nashik who introduces him to the source of stamp papers - the Nashik Security Press.

episodes.title: Mubarak Ho Aapko Stamp Paper Hua Hain
episodes.description: Abdul formulates a strategy to get the management of the Nashik Press on his side and facilitates the promotion of their top bureaucrat. He gets the original machines, dyes and papers from the press and starts printing stamp papers. Although he expands his business, he soon learns that, to truly flourish, he must wipe out his biggest competitor.

episodes.title: I Love You
episodes.description: By manipulating the shutdown of the press and the supply chain of the Old Custom House, Abdul monopolizes the stamp market. His success having caught the attention of many, Abdul begins to befriend every new and bigger power in the state.

episodes.title: Episode 7
episodes.description: Episode 7 of Scam 2003

episodes.title: Egregious
episodes.description: Tyagi seeks key support in his campaign for bar president. Harvard grad Anaya Shroff struggles to find her footing… and a desk.

episodes.title: Dignity
episodes.description: When a monkey causes a stir on the court premises, the lawyers are moved to strike, leading to a strain on Ananya and her first case.

episodes.title: Aukaat
episodes.description: Sujata tries to drop her “foyer lawyer” status with a new client — a foul-mouthed parrot. When a big-shot lawyer arrives, Tyagi and Bagai hatch a plan.

episodes.title: Touch
episodes.description: Ananya and Sujata scramble to help an inmate fulfill her dream to start a family. Tyagi has an emotional talk with his father, a retired judge.

episodes.title: Biradari
episodes.description: Tyagi and his campaign land in hot water after police and lawyers clash. Ananya and Sujata contend with a fierce woman in the race.

episodes.title: Kutai
episodes.description: Phorey or Tyagi? The election results are finally in — but the twists aren't over yet. Ananya turns counselor for a young woman’s case.

episodes.title: Law vs Justice
episodes.description: Tyagi weighs an important decision that will change the course of his career. PP Sahab and Ananya are pulled into a landmark case.

episodes.title: Return from Hell
episodes.description: Amid global turmoil, just-out-of-prison Max joins his parents in a luxury bunker. There, an unexpected encounter confronts him with his darkest past.

episodes.title: The Greatest Con Ever Pulled on Humanity
episodes.description: As the team celebrates their success, not everyone feels comfortable with how the events unfolded. Rafa reels from Frida's revelations.

episodes.title: I Hate the Rich
episodes.description: A shocked Minerva faces a skeptical team in need of answers. Conflicted by the videos of Max, Asia makes a rash decision but later regrets it.

episodes.title: The Millionaire's Paradox
episodes.description: In a medical crisis, Asia is the only one who can help. Victoria welcomes a distraction as she sends out mayday signals. A call grows in urgency.

episodes.title: The Truth Is Overrated
episodes.description: With pressure mounting, Minerva takes a major gamble before assigning a high-stakes mission. Unable to find Guillermo, Mimi turns to Frida and Victoria.

episodes.title: The Woman of Numbered Days
episodes.description: Asia comes to grips with her true feelings. Max confronts Minerva as she prepares to implement phase three in the bunker. Mimi shows troubling symptoms.

episodes.title: Learn to Live without Me
episodes.description: Under false pretenses, Max unveils his plan. Rafa reveals the real reason behind his past actions while Guillermo prioritizes family and friendship.

episodes.title: Two Minutes without Roxán
episodes.description: Frida doesn't hold back as she delivers some painful truths. As a perfectly curated night unfolds, Max and Asia kick into action.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: Episode 5 of Billionaires' Bunker

episodes.title: Part I
episodes.description: Verónica and Marta's families mourn their disappearance. As the police abandon their search, Isabel manages to corner the man who last saw them.

episodes.title: Part II
episodes.description: Isabel deals with the aftermath of her latest discovery and decides that desperate circumstances call for a dangerous alliance with Rafael.

episodes.title: Part III
episodes.description: Antonio makes a shocking disclosure about that fateful night. As Rafael and the police draw closer to the truth, Isabel's search reaches its end.

episodes.title: Episode 15
episodes.description: Episode 15 of Two Graves

episodes.title: The Pruning
episodes.description: When Ana María returns to Mexico from Los Angeles, her father offers to grant her control of the family tequila empire, to the dismay of her brothers.

episodes.title: The Wake
episodes.description: The Carranza siblings mourn their loss while trying to keep the details of the death a secret from family members, friends and the authorities.

episodes.title: The Coronation
episodes.description: Cecilia decides which of her three children should receive control of Monarca. Ana María negotiates with the company's striking workers.

episodes.title: Filthy Rich
episodes.description: Joaquín retaliates against Ana María when she makes a business decision he vehemently disagrees with. Camila is surprised by Pablo's judgmental friends.

episodes.title: Centennial
episodes.description: Ana María suspects someone is sabotaging the opening of the new Monarca hotel. Ilán's presence at the centennial party creates tension for Andrés.

episodes.title: The Other Reality
episodes.description: Pablo is publicly accused of sexual assault. Camila is involved in the backlash as their parents fight over how to respond. Joaquín meets with Emilio.

episodes.title: Bottom
episodes.description: Ana María and Andrés argue over how to solve various problems, both personal and professional. Meanwhile, Joaquín sets up dinner with the governor.

episodes.title: The Revenge of Tzitzimitl
episodes.description: The agave fields burn and Ana María's investigator looks into whether her brother is to blame. Joaquín proposes removing his sister from Monarca.

episodes.title: Borges' Judas
episodes.description: Andrés comes out to Pablo and suggests he turn himself in. With Rubén's help, Ana María discovers who killed her father. Martin's editor pressures him.

episodes.title: The Harvest
episodes.description: The Carranza family argues over which kind of revenge they should dish out to the traitor who murdered Fausto. The victim count rises.

episodes.title: We All Have Secrets
episodes.description: Power dynamics shift when Cecilia chooses a new CEO for Monarca. Agustín's daughter, Sofía, returns for his funeral. Martin delves into the past.

episodes.title: Rebranding
episodes.description: Pablo turns himself in to the authorities. Martin's book research puts him in danger. Jimena involves Monarca in Fashion Week as part of rebranding.

episodes.title: Playing With Fire
episodes.description: Sofía is suspicious of Cecilia's erratic behavior. Ana María is shocked when she learns more about Alberto. Jimena and Andrés try something new.

episodes.title: To Be or Not To Be
episodes.description: The Carranza siblings attempt to do what's best for their mother, in light of her recent action. Joaquín takes part in a dangerous mission.

episodes.title: Two Houses
episodes.description: Lourdes feels alienated at Gonzalo and Itzel's celebration. Sofía continues to seek answers about Fausto's death, defying her cousins.

episodes.title: Exposed
episodes.description: Andrés goes forward with his plan to expand Monarca Hotels. Sara agrees to meet Pablo and Camila. Joaquín gathers evidence against Pilar.

episodes.title: Till Death Do Us Part
episodes.description: Ana María and Pilar deal with the aftermath of the scandal. The entire Carranza family gathers at the Monarca estate for Gonzalo and Itzel's wedding.

episodes.title: The Executioner
episodes.description: Sofía gives Martin shocking news. As Mexico elects a new president, Monarca's reins — and the allegiances between the Carranza siblings — shift again.

episodes.title: Episode 10
episodes.description: Episode 10 of Monarca

episodes.title: The End's Beginning
episodes.description: Hostile townsfolk and a cunning mage greet Geralt in the town of Blaviken. Ciri finds her royal world upended when Nilfgaard sets its sights on Cintra.

episodes.title: Four Marks
episodes.description: Bullied and neglected, Yennefer accidentally finds a means of escape. Geralt's hunt for a so-called devil goes to hell. Ciri seeks safety in numbers.

episodes.title: Betrayer Moon
episodes.description: Geralt takes on another Witcher's unfinished business in a kingdom stalked by a ferocious beast. At a brutal cost, Yennefer forges a magical new future.

episodes.title: Of Banquets, Bastards and Burials
episodes.description: Against his better judgment, Geralt accompanies Jaskier to a royal ball. Ciri wanders into an enchanted forest. Yennefer tries to protect her charges.

episodes.title: Bottled Appetites
episodes.description: Heedless of warnings, Yennefer looks for a cure to restore what she's lost. Geralt inadvertently puts Jaskier in peril. The search for Ciri intensifies.

episodes.title: Rare Species
episodes.description: A mysterious man tries to entice Geralt to join a hunt for a rampaging dragon, a quest that attracts a familiar face. Ciri questions who she can trust.

episodes.title: Before a Fall
episodes.description: With the Continent at risk from Nilfgaard's rising power, Yennefer revisits her past, while Geralt reconsiders his obligation to the Law of Surprise.

episodes.title: Much More
episodes.description: A terrifying pack of foes lays Geralt low. Yennefer and her fellow mages prepare to fight back. A shaken Ciri depends on the kindness of a stranger.

episodes.title: A Grain of Truth
episodes.description: Geralt sets off with Ciri on a journey that leads him to an old friend. After the Battle of Sodden, Tissaia shows no mercy in her search for information.

episodes.title: Kaer Morhen
episodes.description: Seeking a safe place for Ciri, Geralt heads for home, but danger lurks everywhere — even Kaer Morhen. Yennefer's dreams could be the key to her freedom.

episodes.title: What Is Lost
episodes.description: Impatient with Geralt's methods, Ciri braves major obstacles to prove her mettle. Scheming and suspicion amongst the Brotherhood make Yennefer a target.

episodes.title: Redanian Intelligence
episodes.description: A guest at Kaer Morhen extends a guiding hand to Ciri — and an invitation to Geralt. On the run in Redania, Yennefer seeks safety below ground.

episodes.title: Turn Your Back
episodes.description: As a powerful mage joins the hunt for Ciri, she cuts a deal with Vesemir over his extraordinary discovery. Geralt explores the mystery of the monoliths.

episodes.title: Dear Friend...
episodes.description: A close friend is lost — and another found — as Geralt helps Ciri learn more about her power. Cahir warns Fringilla to focus on their primary mission.

episodes.title: Voleth Meir
episodes.description: Geralt turns to the bard Jaskier for help, Yennefer realizes just how special Ciri is, and tensions rise on the eve of Emperor Emhyr's visit to Cintra.

episodes.title: Family
episodes.description: Geralt faces off with a demon targeting his nearest and dearest while the most powerful players on the Continent ramp up their pursuit of Ciri.

episodes.title: Shaerrawedd
episodes.description: Geralt, Yennefer and Ciri journey to the far reaches of the Continent in search of a safe haven. King Vizimir puts his charming younger brother to use.

episodes.title: Unbound
episodes.description: A shocking discovery awaits Geralt after he obtains information on Rience. Ciri's sense of justice causes problems. Jaskier performs for a royal fan.

episodes.title: Reunion
episodes.description: Geralt seeks magical help from a family friend as Ciri and Yennefer clash over plans for the future. Philippa and Dijkstra scheme to get Vizimir in line.

episodes.title: The Invitation
episodes.description: Yennefer pitches a bold idea to the Brotherhood, Geralt strikes a dangerous deal with a ferryman, and Triss digs into the mystery of the missing novices.

episodes.title: The Art of the Illusion
episodes.description: Yennefer and Geralt step out arm in arm and dressed to kill at a lavish ball, but all is not as it seems during a night of revelry and revelations.

episodes.title: Everybody Has a Plan 'til They Get Punched in the Face
episodes.description: Betrayal and bloodshed rock the conclave when the hunt for Ciri comes to a head. As sides are chosen and enemies unmasked, nothing will ever be the same.

episodes.title: Out of the Fire, Into the Frying Pan
episodes.description: Haunted by faces from the past, Ciri endures the ultimate test of survival on a desperate journey under the harshest of conditions.

episodes.title: The Cost of Chaos
episodes.description: After the fateful events at Aretuza, Geralt and Yennefer struggle to pick up the pieces and reunite their family as war comes to the Continent.

episodes.title: Karm
episodes.description: Karma Talwar's entry into the elite Alibaug circle disturbs high-society queen Indrani Kothari. It soon becomes clear that Karma has a dark past. She is on a mission and has her first target in sight.

episodes.title: Bharosa
episodes.description: Karma begins wooing Ahaan Kothari, so Indrani puts her security head Sameer after her. As Karma plots the downfall of her second target, she meets Vedant, her childhood friend.

episodes.title: Annyaay
episodes.description: Karma's next target is the man who convicted her dad. Indrani's suspicions increase when Ahaan and Karma meet his ex-girlfriend. Meanwhile, his friend Krish makes an entry.

episodes.title: Andhere Raaz
episodes.description: Next, Karma trains her sights on Indrani's trusted psychic healer, who left a deep wound in her as a child. Krish becomes a stumbling block to Ahaan and Karma's relationship.

episodes.title: Hisaab Barabar
episodes.description: Ahaan and Karma finally confront each other. Kaushal panics when Dolly threatens him. Moreover, she finds an interesting photograph in her apartment.

episodes.title: Dil Aur Dimaag
episodes.description: Kaushal is aghast to watch Dolly's video. Krish tells Ahaan about his parent's equation. Deeply shaken, Ahaan joins Bombil Cafe where Vedant becomes his taskmaster.

episodes.title: Vaada
episodes.description: Sameer uncovers a darker secret about Karma's past. While she is living the high life in Alibaug with Ahaan, unbeknownst to her, Ambika Mehra's revenge plan may be at risk.

episodes.title: Episode 1
episodes.description: School ends, summer begins and small-town teens' perfect lives crumble when Elena vanishes. Hidden secrets soon emerge, threatening to ruin everything.

episodes.title: Episode 2
episodes.description: Worried about their friend, Vanessa and the group begin a search in the town. Meanwhile, a social media account claims to be Elena.

episodes.title: Episode 3
episodes.description: The town is left in shock. New DNA evidence surfaces, raising more questions. While others have solid alibis, Giorgio harbors a dangerous secret.

episodes.title: Episode 4
episodes.description: Vanessa's confession sparks an arrest, fueling her guilt. Vera's anger intensifies and her family is consumed with worry. Diana makes a risky move.

episodes.title: Episode 5
episodes.description: As the investigation reveals lies within the rowing team, Vanessa's world shifts as she starts a new job and forms unexpected connections.

episodes.title: Episode 6
episodes.description: Tensions peak and relationships break down. Vanessa uncovers the truth about Elena's pain, and a critical clue shifts the investigation.

episodes.title: American Poison
episodes.description: A group of young American heiresses are changed forever when they're whisked across the Atlantic to London.

episodes.title: Women or Wives
episodes.description: Conchita hosts a raucous country house party. Jinny and Lizzy go head-to-head for the same man. Nan reveals a secret.

episodes.title: The Perfect Duchess
episodes.description: At the exclusive Tintagel ball, Nan considers the prospect of becoming a duchess. Conchita struggles with her mother-in-law's approval.

episodes.title: Homecoming
episodes.description: The girls return to New York for a grand celebration. Nan seeks answers from her family. James begins to manipulate Jinny.

episodes.title: Failed Betrayal
episodes.description: Things unravel during a weekend at Guy's family home, as Nan finds herself feeling torn. Mabel and Honoria get closer.

episodes.title: It's Christmas
episodes.description: The gang head to Scotland for a Christmas getaway. Lizzy makes a confession. James' behavior escalates. Nan faces a hard choice.

episodes.title: First Footing
episodes.description: The Brightlingseas host a New Year's Eve party where the bombshell news is the hot topic. Tensions flare as Theo and Guy's rivalry explodes.

episodes.title: Wedding of the Season
episodes.description: Nan must figure out her path forward. Jinny feels trapped. Mrs. St. George reckons with the state of her family.

episodes.title: The Second Coming
episodes.description: A shattered Noyonika Sengupta ends her long sabbatical to return to work as a junior lawyer after her famous husband Rajiv Sengupta is jailed in a sex and corruption scandal.

episodes.title: Scenes from a Marriage
episodes.description: Noyonika takes up the case of a friend’s son accused of murder. She faces criticism from Malini at work. When Sharad Jhadav spills Rajiv's old secrets, she confronts him.

episodes.title: Winds of Change
episodes.description: At work, Noyonika faces pressure but finds a friend in Sana. She learns about Rajiv's illegal dealings and gets upset with her mother-in-law for taking her kids to meet him in jail.

episodes.title: Dirty Little Lies
episodes.description: When opposition lawyer, Shivani Bahl drags Noyonika's personal life to court, she needs to publicly disclose some scandalous truths to get justice. How will Noyonika handle it all?

episodes.title: Family Secrets
episodes.description: A high-profile couple comes under the police radar for their maid's death. Trying to save them, Noyonika straddles legal boundaries. Meanwhile, Rajiv gets a chance at freedom.

episodes.title: Lifeline
episodes.description: A case of a soon-to-be mother and her at-risk unborn child takes Noyonika and Vishal out of town. Back home, the girls tell Rajiv about the packages the family has been receiving.

episodes.title: Trial by Media
episodes.description: Noyonika gears up to fight against Daksh Rathod. Ilyas has a suggestion for Rajiv. When Rajiv’s lawyer leaves him high and dry, Noyonika finds a solution.

episodes.title: Cloak & Dagger
episodes.description: Noyonika fights tooth and nail for Rajiv with Vishal's help as she struggles with her feelings for the two men. In the end, Rajiv's decision leaves her feeling betrayed again.

episodes.title: Hush Hush
episodes.description: Noyonika faces a tough choice when a young masseuse accuses a revered public figure of sexual assault, caught between the truth and her husband Rajiv's rising political career.

episodes.title: Social Dilemma
episodes.description: Noyonika defends influencer Shanaya in an attempted murder trial. Just as Shanaya's bail is revoked, Ananya reveals a shocking truth, flipping the case upside down.

episodes.title: Bad Marriages, Bad Parents
episodes.description: While Noyonika's parenting is tested, she's blindsided by a sharp opposing lawyer in a case against a builder. At work, as alliances shift, Malini feels her position is threatened.

episodes.title: Split Them Up
episodes.description: Rajiv's campaign suffers when Narayani gains sympathy. As Malini's offer tests Noyonika's loyalty, the firm defends two lovers in a murder case, where one needs to be sacrificed.

episodes.title: Sins of the Father
episodes.description: Noyonika uncovers a conspiracy behind the builder case. After a shocking raid shakes her family, Noyonika confronts Narayani and makes a bold move that could change everything.

episodes.title: We Always Want What We Can't Have
episodes.description: As Noyonika wins the builder case and Rajiv's campaign soars, a secret from the past destroys their marriage. Betrayed but empowered, she chooses truth, closure and a new beginning.

episodes.title: Pilot
episodes.description: After serving 12 hard years for a crime he didn't commit, Detective Charlie Crews is back on the LAPD with a new partner and a new zen attitude.

episodes.title: Tear Asunder
episodes.description: Crews and Reese investigate a bride's murder; Crews realizes that a child may have witnessed the murders for which he was convicted.

episodes.title: Let Her Go
episodes.description: An upscale family man is suspected of killing his wife, and Crews sees his ex-wife for the first time since getting out of jail.

episodes.title: What They Saw
episodes.description: When a wealthy man is found murdered in his bed, Crews befriends the only suspect, a homeless thief camping outside the estate.

episodes.title: The Fallen Woman
episodes.description: When an angel falls from the sky, Crews and Reese's murder investigation leads to a slippery Russian gangster.

episodes.title: Powerless
episodes.description: Fearing that a rapist she met at an AA meeting will strike again, Dani enlists Crews' help to take him down.

episodes.title: A Civil War
episodes.description: The murder of two Iranian American students sparks racial unrest as Crews and Reese race to rescue their kidnapped friend.

episodes.title: Farthingale
episodes.description: While investigating the murder of a bigomist, Crews is suspected for the murder of policeman Ames.

episodes.title: Serious Control Issues
episodes.description: While investigating the case of a murdered homeless girl, Reese and Crews stumble across a child who was kidnapped when he was three.

episodes.title: Dig a Hole
episodes.description: Charlie and Dani track the killer of a Zen Master who was buried alive ten years prior.

episodes.title: Fill It Up
episodes.description: Hoping to take down Jack Reese, Crews finds the Seybolts' murderer, but doesn't succeed in proving who set him up.

episodes.title: Breathing
episodes.description: After taking mindfulness lessons, defense lawyer Björn finds a new way to deal with his main client: a violent crime boss who demands too much of him.

episodes.title: Happiness
episodes.description: Björn figures out how to mindfully dispose of a body while navigating the suspicions of his family, the police and Dragan's underlings.

episodes.title: Fear
episodes.description: As he gets back to his routine to avoid any appearance of guilt, Björn discovers a couple of loose ends he needs to deal with.

episodes.title: Shamelessness
episodes.description: Katharina asks for Björn's help in securing a day care center for Emily. Toni suspects Björn isn't being truthful about Dragan's whereabouts.

episodes.title: Panic
episodes.description: Nicole investigates a series of explosive clues. After being kidnapped by a rival crime boss, Björn sets out to expose Toni's plan.

episodes.title: Brainstorming
episodes.description: It would be easier to just murder everyone, but Björn decides on a more practical solution. Nicole questions Emily about her trip to the lake.

episodes.title: Anger
episodes.description: Caught between Toni and the police, Björn looks for a way to kill two birds with one stone. Boris makes a final demand to see Dragan.

episodes.title: Death
episodes.description: Björn enacts a risky plan to deal with Boris and get Nicole off his back, and it's important to be mindful of every detail.

episodes.title: Diamond of the First Water

episodes.title: Shock and Delight
episodes.description: Simon's apparent courtship of Daphne angers her brother Anthony and threatens to ruin the arrangements he made. Marina opens up to a curious Penelope.

episodes.title: Art of the Swoon
episodes.description: After Daphne catches the eye of a royal suitor, she turns to Simon for relationship advice. Lady Featherington tries to browbeat Marina into marriage.

episodes.title: An Affair of Honor
episodes.description: Daphne receives a stunning gift from Prince Friedrich but soon courts scandal at a ball. Eloise searches for clues to Lady Whistledown's identity.

episodes.title: The Duke and I
episodes.description: To fend off rumors about their garden escapade, Simon and Daphne must make a personal appeal to the queen. Marina's wedlock scheme dismays Penelope.

episodes.title: Swish
episodes.description: On her honeymoon, Daphne discovers just how uninformed she is about the physical aspects of the marital bed. Colin comes to a decision about Marina.

episodes.title: Oceans Apart
episodes.description: Amid accusations of lies and betrayal, a rift forms between the newlyweds, while a deception of another kind could besmirch the Bridgerton family name.

episodes.title: After the Rain
episodes.description: The duke and duchess's season-ending ball signals a turning point for their marriage — and ushers in changes of fortune and fate to those around them.

episodes.title: Capital R Rake

episodes.title: Victory
episodes.description: As guests gather for the Bridgerton's ball, Anthony and Kate clash during a hunting party, Colin revisits the past, and Lady Featherington sets a trap.

episodes.title: An Unthinkable Fate

episodes.title: Forces of Nature

episodes.title: Tick Tock

episodes.title: Romancing Mister Bridgerton

episodes.title: Joining of Hands

episodes.title: Into the Light

episodes.title: Thodi Struggle, Bahut Hustle
episodes.description: Abhijeet, a small-town boy with big dreams, leaves behind Delhi and his modest family for a high-paying job in Mumbai. But between five-star hotels, cutthroat colleagues, and fragile friendships, he learns that survival isn't about playing fair - it's about playing smart. In a city built on ambition, will he lose himself before he finds success?

episodes.title: Roti, Kapda Aur Bathtub Wala Makaan
episodes.description: A week into Fusion Funds and the interns are already facing a work life imbalance. They only have a week to find a house. Tired of staying in small spaces, Abhijeet coerces Saurav to be his flatmate so that they can afford a fancy house. he is even willing to go illegal, but competition always catches up.

episodes.title: Jaisa Dikhunga Waise Bikunga
episodes.description: Abhijeet tries to fit into Mumbai's fast world - new house, new style, new rules. But a clash with a colleague and a tough reality check force him to question if changing on the outside is enough to survive inside. In a city that only rewards the polished, Abhijeet realises the real race has just begun.

episodes.title: Dating Radius: 2 KM
episodes.description: Haunted by an old heartbreak, Abhijeet tries to build the perfect life - dream house, dream date, dream image - even hosting a house party to impress. But when a small lie spirals out of control, he's forced to face a harder truth: some lies don't stay small for long.

episodes.title: Bosses From Hell
episodes.description: Old wounds push Abhijeet and Garima to question the small lies we tell to survive. As friendships crack and hidden games come to light, they must decide: in chasing success, what part of themselves are they willing to lose?

episodes.title: Pehli Kamai Pehla Kand
episodes.description: Abhijeet's first paycheck brings celebration, freedom, and a taste of the life he always dreamed of. But as the high wears off, he and his friends are reminded - some moments lift you higher than ever before, only to change everything the next second.

episodes.title: D Se Dosti, D Se Dhokha
episodes.description: Abhijeet's need to prove himself pushes him to make a selfish move - and it costs him more than he imagined. As friendships shatter and regrets build, he's left facing a brutal truth: in chasing success, sometimes you end up standing alone.

episodes.title: Alladin Ka Credit Card
episodes.description: Ostracised after his selfish move, Abhijeet decides he doesn't need anyone. Chasing validation, he buys his way into a new life with Manisha. But as the nights get louder and the bills heavier, Abhijeet begins to learn - you can fake everything, except feeling less alone.

episodes.title: Internet Wala Love
episodes.description: Abhijeet's dream life starts to crack. As fake friendships slip away and mounting credit card debt closes in, a cruel betrayal forces him to face the truth: you can outrun people, but not the loneliness - or the lies you built around it.

episodes.title: Account Balance: Zero
episodes.description: Crushed by debt, broken friendships, and the threat of losing his home, Abhijeet faces the life he built - and the terrifying question of what's left when it all falls apart.

episodes.title: You're Fired
episodes.description: Abhijeet rebuilds his life from scratch - friendships, trust, and a shot at something real. But when layoffs hit Fusion Funds, he's left fighting for the one thing he can't afford to lose again: a future he finally started believing in.

episodes.description: Ayan and Diana make an odd couple, much to the latter’s displeasure. On the contrary, Subhro is not satisfied with Urmi. How will the couple change situations?

episodes.title: Tumi Ki Amar Choto Pisi?
episodes.description: Subhro is elated to take Urmi for a trip, that she agrees to with much timidity for reasons known to her. Can Diana convince Ayan for a mystery tour as planned?

episodes.title: I Love To Push
episodes.description: Upon reaching the destination, Ayan gets the shock of his life after finding the reason for the trip is a quick episode of couple swapping! Will he go for it?

episodes.title: Parallel Universe
episodes.description: The spree of adventure for Diana and her partner gets a jerk, when some uncalled situations arise, and arrive in the same hotel where the couples are staying!

episodes.title: Meye Dakat!!
episodes.description: Things turn worse for Ayan and Urmi, while Diana and Subhro feel their’s is a perfect match. Are they deciding to call it quits with their respective partners?

episodes.title: What The Fcuk!
episodes.description: It’s time for the couples to face the blows from their better halves, not for better but for worse!

episodes.title: I am Cuckold
episodes.description: Mishka is trying to live up to her strict boss Aditi’s expectations. Meanwhile, both are struggling to fix their marriages with Abir and Anirban, respectively.

episodes.title: Nemey Jachhey Keno
episodes.description: A super angry Aditi's husband is having fun with another woman. Abir tries to convince Mishka to be the hotwife to the bull of his choice.

episodes.title: Fact or Fantasy
episodes.description: Anirban and Mishka end up in a police station while enjoying themselves behind Abir’s back. Abir's reaction does not match his liberal ways.

episodes.title: Karma is a B**ch
episodes.description: Abir and Aditi start to get closer, making Mishka’s life miserable. On the other hand, Anirban realises his true feelings for Mishka.

episodes.title: Me and My Girlfriends
episodes.description: Mishka and Aditi confront Abir and Anirban for all the mess in their lives. Will the two mismatched couples finally find what they want?

episodes.title: Episode 6
episodes.description: Episode 6 of Mismatch

episodes.title: Bedtime Story
episodes.description: RK regrets Nibedita's inability to moan, and Imtiaj his nude painter wife. How will they spice up their sex life?

episodes.title: Double Trouble
episodes.description: The boring sex life pushes the couples to the verge of separation. But there's a solution to the rescue.

episodes.title: Secrets of Batsayana
episodes.description: Milan Baba provides a one stop solution for a spiced up sex life. But what's his secret?

episodes.title: Adalam-Badalam
episodes.description: Milan Baba's workshop revives Nibedita's ability to mourn with Adalam-Badalam.

episodes.title: Anti - Climax
episodes.description: Behind the closed doors of the Ashrama, a larger evil lurks. Can the couples solve the mystery?

episodes.title: Chapter 1
episodes.description: In 1950s Charandaspur, a ritual fails to reach its culmination. In the present day, ex-officer Vikram Singh probes a murder with missing body parts.

episodes.title: Chapter 2
episodes.description: Officer Rea travels to Charandaspur where she meets Ananya. Vikram confronts someone from his past. A masked figure lurks in the forest.

episodes.title: Chapter 3
episodes.description: Shastri, a shadow worshipper, reaches out to Rea with an ominous prediction. Vikram learns more about the mandala symbol and its meaning.

episodes.title: Chapter 4
episodes.description: Haunted by memories of his partner, Vikram teams up with Rea to decode eight mandalas linked to the murders — and to stop a harrowing attack.

episodes.title: Chapter 5
episodes.description: As Rea searches for the princess's identity, she opens up to Vikram about her fears. Ananya takes charge at home, while Jimmy cracks the next code.

episodes.title: Chapter 6
episodes.description: Vyankat's revelations leave Vikram shocked and furious. Upon learning that the next victim could be a child, Rea scrambles into rescue mode.

episodes.title: Chapter 7
episodes.description: In the 1950s, Nandini, a scientist, visits Charandaspur where she meets Rukmini, who brings a sinister warning. Later, she builds a wish-granting device.

episodes.title: Chapter 8
episodes.description: Vikram is kidnapped to be sacrificed to revive Yast. Can Rea follow in her grandmother's footsteps and stop the ritual before it's too late?
